These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
House: futuristic, ranch-style, palace, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is not to the right of the futuristic house##8
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
6. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the ranch-style house##7
8. the chinese and the art-deco house have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the futuristic house have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | palace   | art-deco     | ranch-style | futuristic  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
4 different pets are kept: frog, bird, hedgehog, rat
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
4. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | frog | bird | hedgehog      | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, pilot, journalist, writer
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
3. the pilot is on the left of the journalist##1
4. the pilot is on the far left##1
5. the electrician is on the right of the journalist##1
6. the journalist is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the pilot and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | pilot    | journalist   | electrician    | writer  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

