.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, game, tiparillo, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the game-smoker##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the dannemann-smoker and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | dannemann | tiparillo | fonseca  | game |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

