3. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
4. the american and the person who likes mauve have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who likes blood-red and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the person who likes orange##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
8. the person who likes apricot is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | apricot | orange | mauve | blood-red |
| Nationality   | thai        | indian    | american   | brazilian |

