2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer and the person traveling to san-francisco have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
6. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | venice    | hannover | san-francisco         | liverpool     |
| Sport         | sailing | soccer  | skateboarding | lacrosse |

