4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
8. the person who's sport is swimming is the colombian##1
9. the person who's sport is surfing and the canadian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
