The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, begonia, balloon-flower, daisy
 1. the person drinking lemonade and the person who growsballoon-flower have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 3. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking 7up##7
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 5. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the person drinking mirinda and the person who growsbegonia have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 9. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person who growsdahlia##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
